sequenceDiagram
    participant A as Phone A
    participant B as Phone B

    Note over A: Build local snapshot<br/>(changes since last sync)

    A->>B: POST /api/local-sync/manifest<br/>{ watermark, my snapshot }

    Note over B: Merge A's snapshot<br/>Build response with<br/>B's changes

    B-->>A: { watermark, B's deltas }

    Note over A: Merge B's deltas<br/>Advance watermark

    Note over A,B: Both devices fully synced<br/>in one round-trip
